spec_data.Name: perl-Test-Name-FromLine
spec_data.Description:
Test::Name::FromLine is a testing helper that automatically names each unit
test from its source code declaration, unless it was explicitly named.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 04:57:42 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Automatically name tests from their source code
